            <thetext>The textArea widget should be scrollable.

As we use the native HTML textArea, and this is not scrollable by default on iOS or Android, we have to wrap it with a new composte type: scrollComposite.

The scrollComposite contains a composite, which is the target for scrolling. Scrolling is done via CSS and translate3d(0,0,0).
Any child widgets added to this scroller component. Any methods for adding/removing widgets, delegates to the scroller component.</thetext>
